AYURVEDA

A combination of antiseptic and anti fungal essential oils will keep you and your sacred space fresh and clean. Simply spray on and wipe away negative energy and accumulated toxins. If yoga isn't your thing, no worries - this spray is perfect for your gym bag and locker too! Keep your peaceful calm and centre zone (wherever and whatever that is to you!) safe and trouble free with this spray inspired by yogi's everywhere.
Ingredients: Fractionated Coconut Oil, Distilled Rainwater, Witch Hazel, Frankincense Essential Oil, Tea Tree Essential Oil, Lemongrass Essential Oil, Fir Needle Essential Oil
HIPPIE CHIC
For all you crazy hippies out there, (present company included!) who love the scent of patchouli but don't love being overwhelmed by it, this is for you. We've combined the happy scents of patchouli and sweet orange to mellow things out and keep things light. Use as a body spray, room spray or sacred space spray to stimulate your mind and body!
Ingredients: Fractionated Coconut Oil, Distilled Rainwater, Witch Hazel, Patchouli Essential Oil, Sweet Orange Essential Oil, Clove Essential Oil, Lavender Essential Oil
